\">810058486592</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">INSTANT EMERGENCY LIGHT: Whether you’re hiking, camping or backpacking into the great outdoors, putting together an earthquake survival kit or struck with a blackout power outage at home, the ASR Outdoor 36 or 48 hour survival emergency light wax candle provides indoor or outdoor lighting to keep you and your family safe</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">36 OR 48 HOUR BURN TIME: The candle’s four wick sections each have 12 hours of burn time; They can be burned all together or one at a time, providing a total 48 hours of light, using soy and regular wax; Batteries in flashlights and lanterns are expensive and can fail, while the survival candle offers a dependable indoor outdoor lighting source in any situation and can be used as a candle warmer too</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMPACT LIGHTWEIGHT &amp; PORTABLE: The candle is poured in a durable tin box with lid to keep the candle in good condition; the emergency light candle fits in the palm of your hand, making it easy to pack in a bug out bag, with your camping gear or in a trekking backpack; a must-have item in any survival kit!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SURVIVAL FIRE STARTER: If you have matches on hand, this candle may come in handy as a fire starter if igniting your kindling is proving troublesome; with 36 hours of burning time, getting a roaring fire started at your campsite or emergency fire in the wilderness</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=